title: 20,000 Leagues Under the Sea - mp4 version

sources.title: 20,000 Leagues Under the Sea - mp4 version
sources.description: The Universal Film Manufacturing Company was not known in the silent era as premier producer of motion pictures. In the interest of making this great film more available, I've converted it to an mp4 very close to DVD quality. You can find the MPEG2 (1.6 Gig) version at: http://www.archive.org/details/20000LeaguesUndertheSea
